section(id="features" class="feature_section gradiant padding-top-80 padding-bottom-80")
  div(class="container")
    div(class="section_heading mb-40 align-center")
      img(class="lazy section_icon" alt="features" data-src="/img/shape_46x44@2x.png" width="46px" height="44px")
      h2 Features
    div(class="row feature_wrap")
      div(class="col-md-2 order-md-2")
      div(class="col-md-5 order-md-1")
        ul(class="feature_content feature_left align-right")
          li(class="wow fadeInRight" data-wow-delay="0ms" data-wow-duration="1000ms")
            h3 One-click Set Up
            p The add-on automatically creates a template sheet, data validations, and more with one click.
          li(class="wow fadeInRight" data-wow-delay="0ms" data-wow-duration="1000ms")
            h3 Progressive Syncing
            p Syncing progress is tracked within the document so it can continue where you left off.
          li(class="wow fadeInRight" data-wow-delay="150ms" data-wow-duration="1000ms")
            h3 Pull/Push Mechanisms
            p You can control the syncing progress by pressing Pull/Push buttons.
          li(class="wow fadeInRight" data-wow-delay="0ms" data-wow-duration="1000ms")
            h3 Optimized
            p The add-on is optimized to sync up to 2000 terms per minute per document.
      div(class="col-md-5 order-md-3")
        ul(class="feature_content feature_right align-left")
          li(class="wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-delay="0ms" data-wow-duration="1000ms")
            h3 Resettable
            p You can completely recreate a new document and start over if something goes wrong.
          li(class="wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-delay="0ms" data-wow-duration="1000ms")
            h3 Auto Highlight Changes
            p It automatically highlights edited cells so you can view what have been changed.
          li(class="wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-delay="300ms" data-wow-duration="1000ms")
            h3 View History
            p You can view original values (values before you edit) or edit history to revert changes.
          li(class="wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-delay="300ms" data-wow-duration="1000ms")
            h3 Secure
            p This add-on does not requires you to enter password because it uses expirable API keys.
